original_title: Uchu Sentai Kyuranger Final Live Tour 2018
overview: "Sing, Dance, and let's have Fun!"  A live show that was performed across Japan in March and April of 2018, acting as a final farewell for the cast. It comprises two parts: a scripted show part, and a talk show with the cast. The Lupinrangers and the Patrangers also appear in.
title: Uchu Sentai Kyuranger Final Live Tour 2018
